data.description: This Cozy ranch is situated on a beautiful corner lot. Spacious Living Room and Kitchen with Dining area. Big bathroom with a make up vanity. Large hall closet.  There is so much potential to make it your own. Many updates over the past 5 years including the roof, air condenser unit, HWT, sliding doors in both the kitchen and living room and the living room picture window. In addition to the attached garage the 1 car detached garage was built in 2022. The large lot is a blank slate awaiting your outdoor living ideas. Situated off the bike path that leads into the metro park. Close proximity to the school track and tennis courts. Very close to the waterway for easy access to fishing and boating.  Great spot for anyone looking to enjoy the outdoors and living near the water.
